name: ListCashTransactionLedgerGroups
description:
This service allows you to get a grouped view of the cash transaction ledger, which underlies all cash
transactions, such as received payments, moves between devices and expenses.

By default, you only get access to the cash transaction ledger for your current financial period. If
you have the `ManageCashTransactionLedger` permission, you're also allowed to filter on another financial
period.
